# Direct runtime dependencies for update.py / preview.py.
# Source of truth for human edits. The companion ``requirements.txt``
# next to this file holds the fully-pinned transitive lock (regenerated
# via ``pip-compile requirements.in`` whenever this list changes); CI
# installs from the lock for reproducibility, while developers can edit
# this file to add / remove direct deps.
#
# Floors are intentional: a major bump that breaks the integration
# shape we expect (yfinance dropping ``Ticker.get_info``, Pillow's
# ImageFont API change in 10.0, ...) will fail to install rather than
# explode at runtime in CI.
